title: exit - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: Usage usage: exit [ N ] Exits the command line tool. The argument N is the final exit code returned to the calling process. Return Codes Listed below are the different return codes for the exit command: Code Description Code Description N The value of the supplied argument. 0 If no argument was provided.
